Paper: hep-th/0209166

Date: 2002-09-20

Title: Spin and exotic Galilean symmetry

Authors: C. Duval and P. A.Horvathy

Comments: Revised version

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B547 (2002) 306-312

A slightly modified and regularized version of the non-relativistic limit ofthe relativistic anyon model considered by Jackiw and Nair yields particlesassociated with the twofold central extension of the Galilei group, withindependent spin and exotic structure.